Zorojuro's so strong!

13
00:02:58.620 --> 00:03:01.700
He's keeping pace with Boss Kyoshiro!

14
00:03:03.330 --> 00:03:05.290
Don't do this, ronin.

15
00:03:05.790 --> 00:03:07.920
Who is this guy?!

16
00:03:14.260 --> 00:03:17.640
It seems luck is on my side.

17
